title: SSW Brisbane opening party
eventShortDescription:
SSW Brisbane has just moved to a brand new office and we would like you to help us celebrate! Join us for finger food, drinks and two great lightning talks from SSW's Chief architect, Adam Cogan and International General Manager, Lindsay Corfield.

Speaker: Adam Cogan - Microsoft Regional Director | Scrum Master | Speaker

7 simple steps to building your profile
From your foundation – your blog - to speaking at the biggest events in the world.
Come and hear Adam talk about what works and what doesn’t… and step your way to success.

Speaker: Lindsay Corfield - GM International

5 tips for delivering great projects
